00:17:24.240 --> 00:17:25.960
you can see a little bit of that sauce.

00:17:25.960 --> 00:17:28.910
That sauce is because
sugar's hygroscopic,

00:17:28.910 --> 00:17:30.880
when it mixes with
the strawberries, it's

00:17:30.880 --> 00:17:34.810
drawing out all the moisture in the
strawberries and it's creating a sauce.

00:17:34.810 --> 00:17:36.760
And so that's the other
way in which sugar

00:17:36.760 --> 00:17:38.950
helps make this desert so delicious.

00:17:38.950 --> 00:17:41.770
It makes it sweet and then it
also combines with the liquid

00:17:41.770 --> 00:17:43.540
in the strawberries to make a sauce.

