You actually want to
use this, to repaddle it

00:38:57.640 --> 00:38:59.130
and to make it smooth again.

00:38:59.130 --> 00:39:01.720
It's going to be hard like butter,
because it's mostly butter,

00:39:01.720 --> 00:39:04.760
so you're going to want to bring it
to room temperature and paddle it.

00:39:04.760 --> 00:39:07.760
And it might break, it
might look curdled, but just

00:39:07.760 --> 00:39:10.740
wait until it warms up and then when
you paddle it'll get smooth again,

00:39:10.740 --> 00:39:11.739
and then you can use it.

00:39:16.410 --> 00:39:18.670
Any questions?

